JIRA INTRODUCTION

	What is Jira?

		Jira is a project management tool

		Used for:

			Bug Tracking

			Workflow

			Collaboration / comment

	Jira Itself is NOT a test management tool

		XRAY ADDON:

			Xray addon provides extra features 

			Xray Features:

				Test management tools

				Visibility of testing result

				Requirement coverage visibility (RTM)


	Jira -> Xray or zephyr


	CREATING A TICKET:

		SUMMARY:

			Name of the Ticket (Very brief description)

		ASSINEE:

			Person who will work on the ticket

		REPORTER:

		